-10-05T17:44:07.000Z","msg":"我覺得唔好去搞佢哋嘅鋪頭<br />\n但係可以去出文宣係Twitter上面唱衰佢<br />\n身為一間美國公司竟然係呢一個時刻咁奶共<br />\n向獨裁主義嘅國家同埋非人道嘅國家低頭<br />\n可以煲"},{"pid":"4c2f5cd7172770a85d15c4b9ca21a5bac41ec19a","tid":1627292,"uid":260740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf7556db8406da65b5e41e0122414285cac37977","tid":1627292,"uid":307144,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:25:55.000Z","msg":"唔裝修但可唔可以裝飾？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:44:43.000Z","msg":"Memo 紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66b3239eb81bd586cbe93866b6c2485433f68266","tid":1627292,"uid":260740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4646eb00470db123438c7c477ad2486e8effb24","tid":1627292,"uid":277590,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:39:33.000Z","msg":"佢冇好似美心咁樣詆毁示威者，亦無好似360咁攞刀。<br />\n<br />\n求下手足幫佢做下文宣，罷買抵制啦好無？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:45:19.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n文宣<br />\n特別係喺Twitter同埋IG上<br />\nDefame 佢"},{"pid":"2d519e60e888ff5535ab782338347a3734947df1","tid":1627292,"uid":34144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:03:38.000Z","msg":"聽日見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45e8576809aef3eec7b03473b5f777682c00f5a6","tid":1627292,"uid":34144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d519e60e888ff5535ab782338347a3734947df1","tid":1627292,"uid":34144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:03:38.000Z","msg":"聽日見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:03:55.000Z","msg":"應該話一陣見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb155a5c6d44cf4b6cb5b555556b5d5510a6d9cd","tid":1627292,"uid":55162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:04:44.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n罷買就夠"},{"pid":"8604dc827960d424df0e39dedb2cce180df1205e","tid":1627292,"uid":182802,"like"